				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hey Mujahid, fellow Scholar over here <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
As for Maple Quills and Cailun Paper, just get the 10 woodcrafter
<br />
book and scribe it. It's a bug 'everyone' is using heh.
<br />
The book is sold at Stonestair Byway Crafter instance.
<br />
(far back from docks on the right)
<br />

<br />
First, run to Stonestair Byway and find your Scholar instance.
<br />
(First on the left from docks)
<br />
Get the Sholar Essentials Vol 10-19. (Or one at a time as you go heh)
<br />
The regular books are all in there. Also Sage books.
<br />
Regular books = AppIII recipes. 
<br />

<br />
The icky part:
<br />

<br />
Scholars Advanced Scrolls Vol. 12,14,18 and 19 =Some Adept III recipes.
<br />
Also, to make Adept III spells you need Suzuri Ink and that recipe
<br />
is ONLY in Scholar Refining vol. 11. Rare and expensive.
<br />
More Adept III recipes as well.....
<br />

<br />
Then we have Scholar Accessories Vol 16.
<br />

<br />
I'll continue when I get home from work hehe.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v514/Yuizling/boobs.gif" border="0" />
<br />
^^
<br />
Sig changed due to overwhelming whining 
<br />
about it. ( 3 )</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
